Watch: Uganda's Anti-Homosexuality Bill Will Not Only Kill the Gays But All Their Friends Too - Towleroad, More than gay news. More gay men
 
 
 
 In a brief but extremely informative clip, Rob Tisinai (I've featured his videos before) does an excellent job of pointing out the intricacies and fine print in the Uganda "kill the gays" bill, particularly a certain loophole which puts anyone who associates with someone thought to be gay, or who speaks up for them, at risk of execution.
